graph TB
    subgraph ModelRegistry["Model Registry Component"]
        direction TB
        subgraph CoreAPI["Core API Layer"]
            Proxy["model-registry (proxy)<br/>Go REST API<br/>Port: 8080/TCP"]
        end

        subgraph Controller["Controller Layer"]
            ISVCController["model-registry-controller<br/>Go Controller (controller-runtime)<br/>Ports: 8081/TCP, 8443/TCP"]
        end

        subgraph UILayer["UI Layer"]
            BFF["model-registry-ui (BFF)<br/>Go BFF Server<br/>Port: 8080/TCP"]
            Frontend["model-registry-ui (frontend)<br/>React/TypeScript SPA"]
            Frontend -->|serves via| BFF
        end

        subgraph CatalogLayer["Catalog Layer"]
            CatalogServer["model-catalog-server<br/>Go REST API<br/>Port: 8080/TCP"]
        end

        subgraph Utilities["Utility Components"]
            CSI["storage-initializer (CSI)<br/>Go CLI (KServe Plugin)<br/>Init Container"]
            AsyncJob["async-upload-job<br/>Python K8s Job"]
        end
    end

    %% External Users
    User["Data Scientist / ML Engineer"] -->|browses models| Frontend
    CLI["CLI / API Client"] -->|REST API calls| Proxy
    Dashboard["RHOAI Dashboard"] -->|API consumer| BFF

    %% Internal Flows
    BFF -->|proxies /api/v1/model_registry/*| Proxy
    BFF -->|proxies /api/v1/catalog/*| CatalogServer
    BFF -->|namespace listing, RBAC| K8sAPI["Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP"]
    ISVCController -->|syncs ISVC metadata| Proxy
    ISVCController -->|watches InferenceService CRs| K8sAPI
    CSI -->|resolves model-registry:// URIs| Proxy
    AsyncJob -->|registers artifacts| Proxy

    %% Data Layer
    Proxy -->|metadata CRUD| MySQL["MySQL 8.3+<br/>3306/TCP"]
    Proxy -->|metadata CRUD| PostgreSQL["PostgreSQL 16+<br/>5432/TCP"]
    CatalogServer -->|catalog metadata| CatalogDB["model-catalog-postgres<br/>5432/TCP"]
    CatalogServer -->|model metadata import| HuggingFace["Hugging Face API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS"]

    %% External Services
    AsyncJob -->|push/pull models| OCIRegistry["OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS"]
    AsyncJob -->|download models| S3["S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS"]
    CSI -->|delegates download| ModelStorage["Model Storage<br/>(S3/GCS/OCI)"]

    %% Service Mesh
    IstioGW["Istio Gateway<br/>(kubeflow-gateway)"] -->|VirtualService routing| Proxy
    IstioGW -->|VirtualService routing| CatalogServer
    IstioGW -->|VirtualService routing| BFF

    %% Metrics
    Prometheus["Prometheus"] -->|scrapes /metrics| ISVCController

